<div class="container">
  <div class="row g-5 about-page">
    <h2 class="pb-4 mb-4 border-bottom">
      About
    </h2>
    <h3 class="pb-2 mb-2 mt-3 fst-italic">
      What is cryptocurrency?
    </h3>
    <p class="m-0">
      Cryptocurrency is a type of digital money that:
      </p>
    <ul class="m-0 px-5">
      <li>
        Exists only online — no physical coins or bills.
      </li>
      <li>
        Uses blockchain technology to work without banks or governments.
      </li>
      <li>
        Is secured by cryptography, making it nearly impossible to counterfeit.
      </li>
      <li>
        The first and most well-known cryptocurrency is Bitcoin (BTC), launched in 2009 by someone using the name Satoshi Nakamoto.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="pb-2 mb-2 mt-5 fst-italic">
      What is the impact to our world?
    </h3>
    <p class="m-0">
      Cryptocurrency is a type of digital money that:
      </p>
    <ol class="m-0 px-5">
      <li>
        Changing Finance (DeFi)
        <ul>
            <li>
                Decentralized finance (DeFi) lets people lend, borrow, and earn interest without banks.
            </li>
            <li>
                Billions of dollars now move through DeFi platforms like Uniswap, Aave, and Compound.
            </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        Empowering the Unbanked
        <ul>
            <li>
                Over 1 billion people globally have no access to banks.
            </li>
            <li>
                With just a phone and internet, they can now use crypto for savings, payments, and transfers.
            </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        Enabling Fast, Cheap Transfers
        <ul>
            <li>
                Crypto makes it possible to send money across borders in minutes, for pennies, compared to traditional remittance fees.
            </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        Creating New Digital Economies
        <ul>
            <li>
                New jobs in Web3, gaming (Play-to-Earn), NFTs, and crypto trading are changing how people earn and invest.
            </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        Challenging Inflation and Fiat Money
        <ul>
            <li>
                In countries with high inflation (e.g., Venezuela, Zimbabwe), people use crypto like Bitcoin or stablecoins to preserve their savings.
            </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        Fueling Innovation
        <ul>
            <li>
                Blockchains allow for smart contracts, NFTs, DAOs, and digital identity — changing the way we think about ownership, trust, and governance.
            </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <h3 class="pb-2 mb-2 mt-5 fst-italic">
      What can our dashboard bring to you?
    </h3>
    <p class="m-0">
      Provides you with ease-of-access to the real-time details of all cryptocurrencies
      </p>
